# Variables
@api_url = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Health check
GET {{api_url}}/health

### Register organizer
POST {{api_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "organizer@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "role": "organizer"
}

### Register normal user
POST {{api_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "role": "user"
}
